OL,3,CCampaigner seeks High Court claim
OL,4,Cagainst the Gambling Commission
OL,6,FA gambling reform campaigner has filed
OL,7,Fa legal claim with the High Court to
OL,8,Fcontest the Gambling Commission's
OL,9,Fdecision not to take regulatory action
OL,10,Fagainst Betfair.
OL,12,FCampaigner Annie Ashton's husband Luke
OL,13,FAshton, from Leicester, took his own
OL,14,Flife in 2021 having racked up debts of
OL,15,F#18,000.
OL,17,FAn inquest in 2023 found that he died
OL,18,Fas a result of his gambling disorder.
OL,19,FDespite his debts, the 40-year-old was
OL,20,Fnot deemed by Betfair to be a problem
OL,21,Fgambler.
