OL,3,CCampaigner seeks High Court claim
OL,4,Cagainst the Gambling Commission
OL,6,FAnnie is represented by partner Merry
OL,7,FVarney and solicitor Dan Webster, with
OL,8,FHelena Hart-Watson, in Leigh Day's
OL,9,FHuman Rights department, as well as
OL,10,Fbarrister Jesse Nicholls of Matrix
OL,11,FChambers.
OL,13,FThe Gambling Commission has said:
OL,15,F''With legal proceedings in process we
OL,16,Fare limited in what we can say.
OL,18,F"However, we vigorously disagree with
OL,19,Fany claims we have failed to
OL,20,Fadequately regulate operators or
OL,21,Fprotect people from harm.
