OL,3,CCampaigner seeks High Court claim
OL,4,Cagainst the Gambling Commission
OL,6,F"We take robust action against
OL,7,Fgambling businesses.
OL,9,F"In the last four years we have taken
OL,10,Faction against 56 operators who have
OL,11,Fpaid out #105m for failing to protect
OL,12,Fconsumers.
OL,14,F"Just this week we fined an operator
OL,15,F#98,400 for failing to check on the
OL,16,Fwelfare of a customer who spent nearly
OL,17,F#2,000 over two days.
OL,19,F"We understand this is sensitive
OL,20,Fmatter and our condolences go to Mrs
OL,21,FAshton.''
