OL,3,CCampaigner seeks High Court claim
OL,4,Cagainst the Gambling Commission
OL,6,FA Betfair spokesperson said: "We hold
OL,7,Fourselves to the highest standards in
OL,8,Fthe industry and we reiterate our
OL,9,Fsincere condolences to Mrs Ashton and
OL,10,Fher family over this tragic case.
OL,12,F"We have made a number of improvements
OL,13,Fto our player protections since early
OL,14,F2021.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, due to live legal
OL,17,Fproceedings we are unable to comment
OL,18,Fany further at this time."
